steps.name: Given I am on the HOME page
When I clock in the timesheet with PIN "0210"
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('0', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('2', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('1', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('0', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title') }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'CONFIRM', exact: true })
Then I should see the employee "Late Turn" in the employee list
When I hold the "Late Turn" employee two seconds
Then I should see the "TURN" Adjustment
When I click on the "Add Late Turn" in turn adjustment
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Adjust Turn"
And I click on the "INCREASE" button in the popup dialog
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see Employee "Late Turn" with "Turn: 20.0" in the employee list
